{
  "title": "Sugar stress and lack of prep",
  "slug": "sugar-stress-and-lack-of-prep",
  "publishedAt": "2021-11-05T06:08:00.000Z",
  "excerpt": "That's usually the #1 reason why people who start diets fall off them, and it's surprisingly simple to fix.",
  "image": "",
