  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That's usually the #1 reason why people who start diets fall off them, and it's surprisingly simple to fix.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Quit",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " consuming sugar.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Don't",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " get stressed.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Stop",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " eating aimlessly.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Of course, simple doesn't make it easy. For many people, it's astonishingly difficult to routinely do one of these tasks, let alone all three.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Which is, in itself, part the problem. Because we’re working from the assumption that we need to give up three things at once.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Dieting (correctly) isn’t about ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " doing ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "all",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " of the things that could wreck your long-term progress. It’s about consistently doing a simple set of things that could enable it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Things like:",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Detoxing",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " your kitchen (and keeping it that way).",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Doing things",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " that make you feel less stressed. Like exercise. Or play.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Cooking",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " your meals at home. And planning your meals ahead.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Behavioral change—and all change is behavioral change—isn’t really about the things you give up, and more about the things—the habits—you replace them with.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The trick is doing them long enough for them to begin to stick.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}